    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上《<strong>风暴之刃</strong>》的征程，在这场动作冒险中，传统与激烈战斗交相辉映。扮演一位年轻战士，在穿越古老废墟与遗忘神殿的世界中完成神圣的成年礼。你的使命：追猎并击败传说中的守护者——这些守护着远古秘密的生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/9b1ef3bfb6b097adc74d59f627814956.poster.avif?t=1771615952\" width=508 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/9b1ef3bfb6b097adc74d59f627814956.webm?t=1771615952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/9b1ef3bfb6b097adc74d59f627814956.mp4?t=1771615952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >唤醒古老祭坛，汲取废墟中的神秘能量，用打败的敌人的精髓强化你的剑刃。每场胜利都让你更接近成为传奇——夺取对手的遗物作为征服的证明。掌握战斗艺术——躲避守护者的无情攻击，以狂暴的精准反击摧毁他们的防御。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/198e3cefa8e8290961fa9c1beccaad70.poster.avif?t=1771615952\" width=508 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/198e3cefa8e8290961fa9c1beccaad70.webm?t=1771615952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/198e3cefa8e8290961fa9c1beccaad70.mp4?t=1771615952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>风暴之刃重制版</strong>》携其标志性的流畅剑术战斗回归，如今比以往任何时候都更精准。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动感十足、充满动作感的剑术战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级武器，赋予其神秘力量</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对抗无情的敌人与巨大的守护者</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索被大自然吞噬的丛林和被时间遗忘的废墟</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与来自世界各地的战士们一争高下，争夺荣耀</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握战士之道，解锁成就</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保存系统记录您的进度</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全面支持控制器，带来更佳体验</p></li></ul>",
